00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:04.980
Khun Yai.

00:03:06.060 --> 00:03:07.260
What’s the matter?

00:03:08.220 --> 00:03:10.540
Are you ready? Let’s go then.

00:03:11.660 --> 00:03:12.620
Wait.

00:03:13.700 --> 00:03:15.100
Where are you going?

00:03:15.730 --> 00:03:18.140
Aren't you going out to take care of something?

00:03:18.140 --> 00:03:19.740
Sin and I will drop you off.

00:03:20.930 --> 00:03:22.660
How did you know?

00:03:25.220 --> 00:03:26.340
Kaew.

00:03:28.780 --> 00:03:30.420
Are you leaving, dear?

00:03:30.530 --> 00:03:31.329
Yes, Mum.

00:03:32.740 --> 00:03:37.500
I bumped into Khun Yai on his way out, and he heard me saying that you’re also leaving.

00:03:37.500 --> 00:03:39.260
So, he volunteered to drop you off.

00:03:42.060 --> 00:03:44.730
Khun Yai, Khun Kaew…the car is ready.

00:03:45.860 --> 00:03:47.140
Let’s go then.

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:48.660
Wait.

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:52.180
I told Ruedee I’d go with her.

00:03:55.329 --> 00:03:56.579
She’s probably here by now.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:58.420
Please excuse me.

00:03:59.329 --> 00:04:00.580
I'm going then, Mum.

00:04:01.260 --> 00:04:01.620
Yes.

00:04:01.620 --> 00:04:02.460
Goodbye.

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:14.000
Kaew.

00:04:14.260 --> 00:04:16.579
Ruedee, let’s go.

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:22.019
Oh, hello there, Khun Yai.

00:04:22.940 --> 00:04:24.380
- Come.
- Let’s go.

00:04:29.660 --> 00:04:30.740
Thank you.

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:35.460
Awww.

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:40.659
You’re relieved, aren’t you?

00:04:44.460 --> 00:04:45.560
What are you talking about?

00:04:46.760 --> 00:04:49.330
That Miss Ruedee’s brother isn’t coming with her.

00:04:58.020 --> 00:04:59.700
Awww.

00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:11.380
Why does Ajarn Kitti want you to pick up your drawing tonight?

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:15.100
I wonder too, Ruedee. There’s no one here.

00:05:20.100 --> 00:05:21.140
It’s not locked.

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:27.500
So quiet.

00:05:28.100 --> 00:05:29.660
Isn’t anybody here today?

00:05:29.820 --> 00:05:30.820
Yeah.

00:05:42.900 --> 00:05:45.020
Hello, Sister.

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:48.159
Isn’t it a semester break, what are you two doing here?

00:05:49.340 --> 00:05:51.600
I’m here to get my drawing back from Ajarn.

00:05:53.500 --> 00:05:55.780
Is it Ajarn Kitti, my friend?

00:05:58.530 --> 00:06:00.620
He’s not in the office though.

00:06:02.760 --> 00:06:03.900
That’s weird.

00:06:04.200 --> 00:06:06.500
Didn’t he tell you to come see him tonight?

00:06:08.940 --> 00:06:09.930
I don’t know too.

00:06:10.100 --> 00:06:12.580
But if it’s Kaewta’s drawing,

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:14.100
I saw it on his table.

00:06:16.100 --> 00:06:18.620
Let’s go get it then.

00:06:18.860 --> 00:06:20.500
He’s probably put it there for you.

00:06:21.330 --> 00:06:22.580
- Come.
- Let’s go.

00:06:22.660 --> 00:06:23.860
Please excuse us.

00:06:29.160 --> 00:06:30.360
Wait, Ruedee.

00:06:34.530 --> 00:06:36.140
What is it?

00:06:38.330 --> 00:06:40.300
I was hoping you could help me with something.

00:06:41.930 --> 00:06:44.900
But I have to go with Kaewta.

00:06:45.930 --> 00:06:47.140
It’s all right, Ruedee.

00:06:48.130 --> 00:06:50.260
Go help your cousin.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:55.130
Also, Ajarn Kitti isn’t in his office, I can go there alone.

00:06:56.860 --> 00:06:58.380
Are you sure?

00:07:08.900 --> 00:07:11.700
So, how can I help you?

00:07:58.659 --> 00:07:59.940
Ajarn Kitti.

00:08:10.260 --> 00:08:11.340
Hello.

00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:16.860
What are you doing here?

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:22.860
I thought you told me to pick up my drawing today.

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:25.400
Did I say that?

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:29.860
How come I couldn’t remember it?

00:08:31.700 --> 00:08:33.500
You really told me to come today.

00:08:38.460 --> 00:08:43.580
Or perhaps, you’re not here to pick up your drawing.

00:08:52.860 --> 00:08:54.060
Here, take this pill.

00:08:55.460 --> 00:08:56.260
Thanks.

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:57.800
And water.

00:09:03.700 --> 00:09:06.530
Suddenly, I got cramps in my stomach and I could barely walk.

00:09:08.930 --> 00:09:14.360
But you were looking quite fine earlier.

00:09:20.900 --> 00:09:22.000
I was holding it in.

00:09:22.460 --> 00:09:24.500
I don’t want anyone to see it when I’m weak.

00:09:26.100 --> 00:09:26.900
Is that so?

00:09:27.500 --> 00:09:32.140
Since you’re feeling better now, I’m going to go check on Kaewta.

00:09:41.420 --> 00:09:41.860
Sister!

00:09:43.730 --> 00:09:44.530
Sister!

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:45.760
Sister!

00:09:46.540 --> 00:09:48.460
Are you all right?

00:09:48.530 --> 00:09:50.700
My stomach hurts so much.

00:09:50.700 --> 00:09:51.940
Oh, dear.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:57.500
What are you saying?

00:09:58.530 --> 00:10:00.540
Come on, Kaewta.

00:10:02.330 --> 00:10:06.460
You’re also interested in me, aren’t you?

00:10:07.260 --> 00:10:08.380
No, I’m not!

00:10:10.600 --> 00:10:13.940
If you want a good grade, just be a good boy for me.

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:21.900
I’ll tell Chancellor that you’re using this kind of thing to threaten your students.

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:24.660
Are you threatening me?

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:27.900
I’m not.

00:10:28.660 --> 00:10:29.860
I will definitely do it.

00:10:40.400 --> 00:10:41.860
How mean.

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:47.740
Don’t tell me you also don’t like it too.

00:10:48.860 --> 00:10:50.060
Where’s my drawing?

00:10:53.060 --> 00:10:58.020
If you don’t give it to me, I’m going to tell Chancellor.

00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:02.220
Chancellor this, chancellor that.

00:11:03.930 --> 00:11:04.730
Over there.

00:11:21.130 --> 00:11:22.340
No.

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:06.820
So beautiful.

00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:10.380
Your beauty surpasses all others, Kaewta.

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:23.900
Kaew!

00:12:24.100 --> 00:12:24.800
Kaew!

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:25.530
Kaew!

00:12:25.530 --> 00:12:26.200
Khun Yai!

00:12:26.200 --> 00:12:27.340
Kaew is in danger.

00:12:27.460 --> 00:12:28.220
You can’t go, Khun Yai!

00:12:28.220 --> 00:12:29.500
Let me go!

00:12:30.330 --> 00:12:32.330
Are you going to let that scumbag hurt Kaew?

00:12:42.200 --> 00:12:43.420
I’ll go instead!

00:12:43.500 --> 00:12:45.060
Your spirit isn’t strong enough!

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:46.860
- I don’t care!
- But..

00:12:47.400 --> 00:12:49.300
Khun Yai! Khun Yai!

00:12:49.760 --> 00:12:50.560
Khun Yai!

00:13:01.800 --> 00:13:04.420
You, bastard! Son of a bitch!

00:13:04.600 --> 00:13:05.820
Get off me!

00:13:05.860 --> 00:13:07.300
I’m going to kill you!

00:13:17.500 --> 00:13:18.460
Khun Yai!

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:19.600
Khun Yai!

00:13:20.060 --> 00:13:21.380
Stop it, Khun Yai!

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:22.400
That’s enough, Khun Yai!

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:26.500
Let me go, Saen! He hurts the person I love. I’m going to kill him!

00:13:27.200 --> 00:13:29.820
But you’re committing more sins this way.

00:13:30.060 --> 00:13:32.360
Those merits you have done up until now would mean nothing.

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:33.500
Khun Yai!

00:13:37.530 --> 00:13:40.580
Go! Get out of my face before I’ll strangle you to death!

00:13:41.260 --> 00:13:42.060
Out!!

00:13:47.900 --> 00:13:49.580
Khun Yai, Khun Yai!

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:51.000
Khun Yai.

00:13:53.730 --> 00:13:54.900
Khun Yai.

00:13:55.730 --> 00:13:56.530
Kaew.

00:13:57.660 --> 00:13:58.460
Kaew.

00:13:59.700 --> 00:14:00.500
Saen.

00:14:01.530 --> 00:14:05.380
Kaew. Saen, go help him.

00:14:06.400 --> 00:14:08.860
But you’re…

00:14:08.930 --> 00:14:11.060
Saen! Go help him!

00:14:12.900 --> 00:14:13.780
Yes, sir.

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:21.980
Khun Kaew.

00:14:22.530 --> 00:14:23.740
Khun Kaew.

00:14:44.860 --> 00:14:47.300
Kaew, can you hear me?

00:14:48.020 --> 00:14:51.140
Kaew, can you hear me?

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:52.160
Kaew.

00:14:52.760 --> 00:14:53.560
Kaew.

00:14:55.100 --> 00:14:56.300
He finally came to.

00:14:56.700 --> 00:14:57.140
Kaew.

00:14:57.140 --> 00:14:58.180
Ruedee.

00:14:58.180 --> 00:14:59.660
Easy there.

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:00.700
Khun Kaew.

00:15:04.260 --> 00:15:05.260
How are you feeling?

00:15:07.300 --> 00:15:11.220
Fortunately, Sin decided to follow us and warn me about you.

00:15:11.860 --> 00:15:14.260
So, we came looking for you at Ajarn Kitti’s office.

00:15:14.620 --> 00:15:18.540
And found you here alone unconscious.

00:15:20.560 --> 00:15:21.740
Ajarn Kitti…

00:15:26.060 --> 00:15:27.140
What is it, Kaew?

00:15:27.140 --> 00:15:30.340
Kaew, why did you faint all of a sudden?

00:15:30.560 --> 00:15:32.420
I didn’t faint on my own, Ruedee.

00:15:33.200 --> 00:15:34.000
What happened?

00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:38.760
The drawing.

00:15:48.130 --> 00:15:49.260
No.

00:15:53.800 --> 00:15:54.980
It’s not here!

00:15:58.460 --> 00:16:00.660
Kaew, what are you looking for?

00:16:00.900 --> 00:16:02.700
That’s right, please tell me, I’ll help look for it.

00:16:03.930 --> 00:16:06.780
My drawing, it’s gone, Ruedee!

00:16:07.060 --> 00:16:08.020
It’s gone!

00:16:08.260 --> 00:16:10.180
Kaew.

00:16:10.180 --> 00:16:12.940
Please calm down. It’s all right, Kaew.

00:16:12.940 --> 00:16:16.380
Don’t worry, Kaew. Please calm down.

00:16:16.700 --> 00:16:18.700
Let’s calm down first.

00:16:19.100 --> 00:16:20.860
- Calm down, Kaew.
- Ruedee.

00:16:22.460 --> 00:16:23.260
Kaew.

00:16:23.860 --> 00:16:25.000
Brother, you’re here.

00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.860
Our driver went to call me, so I came rushing here.

00:16:28.560 --> 00:16:29.360
Kaew.

00:16:29.900 --> 00:16:30.860
Kaew.

00:16:31.660 --> 00:16:32.760
What happened?

00:16:34.730 --> 00:16:36.460
Please calm down, Kaew.

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:37.660
Please calm down, Kaew.

00:16:38.930 --> 00:16:40.100
It’s going to be all right.

00:16:40.400 --> 00:16:41.540
Everything will be all right, Kaew.

00:16:50.960 --> 00:16:51.960
Easy there.

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:53.500
Be careful, Khun Kaew.

00:16:53.620 --> 00:16:55.060
You don’t have to carry me.

00:16:55.500 --> 00:16:57.500
I’m fine, Ruedee.

00:16:57.740 --> 00:17:00.340
Don’t be stubborn.

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:06.260
Do you know how worried my brother and I are?

00:17:06.930 --> 00:17:07.730
Thank you.

00:17:09.800 --> 00:17:11.300
Thank you, Chai.

00:17:12.300 --> 00:17:13.099
Yes.

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:18.660
I would’ve felt so bad if anything happened to you.

00:17:21.819 --> 00:17:26.960
So, what are you going to do about Ajarn Kitti?

00:17:30.730 --> 00:17:32.860
You get punished when you do something wrong.

00:17:34.930 --> 00:17:37.330
I’m going to report this to our chancellor.

00:17:37.580 --> 00:17:41.860
Good, someone like that shouldn’t be teaching anyone again in his life.

00:17:43.260 --> 00:17:46.100
- Oh, hello there.
- Hello, Mother Chan.

00:17:46.100 --> 00:17:47.660
You’re back, dear?

00:17:48.660 --> 00:17:49.300
Yes.

00:17:49.300 --> 00:17:53.380
What’s wrong? You’re burning up.

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:56.300
I’m fine, Mum.

00:17:56.900 --> 00:17:58.820
Just a little tired, that’s all.

00:18:01.800 --> 00:18:05.580
Kaew, go get some rest then.

00:18:05.730 --> 00:18:07.060
We’re leaving.

00:18:07.260 --> 00:18:10.300
Thank you both of you so much…for dropping him off.

00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:11.900
You’re welcome.

00:18:14.500 --> 00:18:15.780
Let’s go home, Brother.

00:18:17.100 --> 00:18:18.860
But Ruedee…

00:18:19.260 --> 00:18:20.260
Let’s go.

00:18:22.460 --> 00:18:24.300
Please excuse us then.

00:18:25.530 --> 00:18:26.160
Goodbye.

00:18:26.160 --> 00:18:26.960
Goodbye.

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:27.800
Bless you, dear.

00:18:27.900 --> 00:18:29.000
Goodbye, Sin.

00:18:29.730 --> 00:18:30.700
Goodbye, Chai.

00:18:41.020 --> 00:18:42.620
I’ll get you some medicine.

00:18:43.260 --> 00:18:44.060
Yes.

00:18:45.180 --> 00:18:46.340
Please don’t worry.

00:18:49.160 --> 00:18:50.000
Sin.

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:52.540
Do you need anything, Khun Kaew?

00:18:54.300 --> 00:18:55.500
Nothing.

00:18:56.660 --> 00:18:57.560
I’m just curious.

00:18:58.700 --> 00:19:01.700
Curious? What are you curious about?

00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:05.700
How did you follow me to the university?

00:19:07.760 --> 00:19:09.980
Well, I…

00:19:12.600 --> 00:19:13.860
And Khun Yai too.

00:19:14.400 --> 00:19:17.300
Khun Yai? What about him?

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:25.220
Before I passed out, I saw Khun Yai there.

00:19:31.460 --> 00:19:32.740
It was really him, wasn’t it?

00:19:37.200 --> 00:19:40.220
Yes, Khun Yai was there to help you.

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:47.060
Khun Yai was there. It was really him.

00:19:47.930 --> 00:19:52.740
I’m sorry, Khun Yai. But if I had to keep it from him any longer,

00:19:53.660 --> 00:19:56.100
my head could’ve burst from frustration.

00:19:57.060 --> 00:20:00.220
So…where is Khun Yai right now?

00:20:00.780 --> 00:20:02.220
I’m going to thank him.

00:20:02.220 --> 00:20:03.060
You can’t.

00:20:03.060 --> 00:20:06.060
Khun Yai isn’t willing to see anyone right now.

00:20:06.660 --> 00:20:07.460
Why?

00:20:10.260 --> 00:20:11.860
You can’t go, Khun Kaew!

00:20:11.860 --> 00:20:13.660
Khun Yai is badly injured.

00:20:15.530 --> 00:20:17.100
He’s injured?

00:20:18.260 --> 00:20:19.760
Is it because he helped me?

00:20:20.300 --> 00:20:20.730
Khun Kaew.

00:20:20.730 --> 00:20:21.620
I’m going to see him!

00:20:21.620 --> 00:20:22.660
- You can’t.
- Move!

00:20:22.660 --> 00:20:23.580
You can’t go!

00:20:24.060 --> 00:20:25.620
Khun Kaew!

00:20:25.860 --> 00:20:26.660
Khun Kaew!

00:20:26.700 --> 00:20:28.060
Kaew!

00:20:28.360 --> 00:20:29.300
Khun Kaew.

00:20:30.200 --> 00:20:32.940
Are you all right? Let’s get you to your room.

00:20:33.130 --> 00:20:34.540
- Let’s go.
- Oh, dear.

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:39.540
There you go.

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:46.540
You’re burning hot, dear.

00:20:47.130 --> 00:20:49.980
Let’s take some pills and get some sleep.

00:20:49.980 --> 00:20:51.420
Give me your hand.

00:21:05.400 --> 00:21:08.860
Khun Yai…Khun Yai is also sick, Mum.

00:21:09.860 --> 00:21:12.160
Oh, is he not feeling well too?

00:21:14.130 --> 00:21:14.930
Yes.

00:21:20.160 --> 00:21:21.460
I’ll go check on him.

00:21:21.700 --> 00:21:22.860
- Khun Kaew.
- No, no.

00:21:22.860 --> 00:21:24.980
No, no. Sit down, dear.

00:21:24.980 --> 00:21:27.900
You can barely walk yourself, how are you going to help him?

00:21:27.960 --> 00:21:31.540
Please don’t worry, Khun Kaew. My da…

00:21:34.360 --> 00:21:37.740
I mean, Saen is looking after Khun Yai right now. He’ll be better soon.

00:21:39.900 --> 00:21:41.140
Really?

00:21:42.160 --> 00:21:44.460
Will he be all right soon?

00:21:45.300 --> 00:21:46.100
Yes.

00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:53.660
My poor baby. You’re this sick yourself but still worry about someone else.

00:21:54.100 --> 00:21:55.980
Now, go get some rest, dear.

00:21:56.260 --> 00:21:57.060
Come.

00:21:57.860 --> 00:21:58.820
Let me help.

00:21:59.260 --> 00:22:00.400
Thank you.

00:22:01.260 --> 00:22:02.340
Let’s go.

00:22:15.700 --> 00:22:17.180
Not again.

00:22:17.500 --> 00:22:21.140
You never listen to me. That’s why.

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:23.740
Dad.

00:22:23.740 --> 00:22:25.980
Sin, how’s Khun Kaew?

00:22:29.160 --> 00:22:30.660
How’s Kaew?

00:22:33.130 --> 00:22:34.820
He’s feeling better.

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:36.860
Miss Chan is looking after him right now.

00:22:40.220 --> 00:22:41.130
Kaew.

00:22:42.700 --> 00:22:44.540
He’ll be fine.

00:22:44.660 --> 00:22:46.700
It’s you who is in trouble.

00:22:46.760 --> 00:22:47.900
That’s right.

00:22:48.400 --> 00:22:49.860
You must get well soon.

00:22:52.100 --> 00:22:58.260
Khun Kaew saw you when you were there to help him.

00:23:01.700 --> 00:23:02.340
Really?

00:23:02.340 --> 00:23:03.540
Yes, Dad.

00:23:05.330 --> 00:23:07.260
Khun Kaew is very worried about you, Khun Yai.

00:23:07.730 --> 00:23:12.140
Once he’s fully recovered, I’m sure he’s going to ask if he could see you.

00:25:21.700 --> 00:25:23.180
Why did you stop?

00:25:24.360 --> 00:25:25.980
I was enjoying it.

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:32.100
You keep staring like that, who’d be able to dance?

00:25:37.160 --> 00:25:43.540
If you’re done with the practising, shall we do something else then?

00:25:45.460 --> 00:25:50.020
Khun Yai! It’s still early.

00:25:52.160 --> 00:25:53.580
What were you thinking?

00:26:43.330 --> 00:26:45.180
I love you, Kaewta.

00:26:50.300 --> 00:26:54.700
Please tell me if you also feel the same.

00:27:00.130 --> 00:27:03.620
Isn’t it quite obvious already?

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:08.980
Still, I want to hear it from you.

00:27:09.620 --> 00:27:11.620
Please say it for me.

00:27:18.400 --> 00:27:21.700
After you come back from a business trip this time,

00:27:22.660 --> 00:27:23.860
I’ll say it.

00:27:24.800 --> 00:27:28.100
Really? Do you promise?

00:27:34.020 --> 00:27:40.530
I promise. When you come back, I’ll say it.

00:28:25.330 --> 00:28:31.140
What the heck? What kind of dream was that?

00:28:45.460 --> 00:28:46.660
That’s right.

00:28:48.730 --> 00:28:49.860
Khun Yai.

00:29:01.160 --> 00:29:03.800
What about your son? How is he?

00:29:05.060 --> 00:29:06.900
He’s not feeling well today, sir.

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:11.380
Karma is after him for he’s bound by a promise.

00:29:13.530 --> 00:29:14.330
Pardon?

00:29:15.330 --> 00:29:21.740
Tell Kaew, your son, to come to me if he wants to know anything.

00:29:22.260 --> 00:29:24.180
I will help him.

00:29:26.900 --> 00:29:27.820
Yes, sir.

00:29:28.930 --> 00:29:30.060
Bless you.

00:29:42.530 --> 00:29:45.780
Khun Yai! Khun Yai!

00:29:52.360 --> 00:29:53.460
Khun Yai!

00:30:02.730 --> 00:30:04.500
I’m going in then.

00:30:06.420 --> 00:30:07.540
Kaew.

00:30:18.330 --> 00:30:19.540
He’s not here?

00:30:21.760 --> 00:30:23.780
Kaew, are you up, dear?

00:30:26.300 --> 00:30:28.340
How’s your fever? Is it better?

00:30:31.060 --> 00:30:32.900
I’m good now, Mum.

00:30:34.700 --> 00:30:36.260
What are you doing here?

00:30:39.000 --> 00:30:40.580
Where’s Khun Yai, Mum?

00:30:41.930 --> 00:30:44.460
Isn’t he in his room?

00:30:46.360 --> 00:30:47.540
No.

00:30:50.060 --> 00:30:51.860
I met Sin this morning.

00:30:52.100 --> 00:30:54.340
He told me Khun Yai is resting in his room.

00:30:56.600 --> 00:30:58.420
So…where are Sin and Saen?

00:30:59.560 --> 00:31:03.300
I’m also looking for them…and Nanny Yam too.

00:31:05.330 --> 00:31:08.100
How odd, where do they all disappear to?

00:31:13.300 --> 00:31:14.500
Or maybe…

00:31:21.660 --> 00:31:24.620
You couldn’t even handle just a weak lad like him.

00:31:24.620 --> 00:31:26.340
How dare you show your face here?

00:31:26.960 --> 00:31:31.330
Who would’ve thought the man in the portrait would suddenly appear to save Kaewta?

00:31:32.960 --> 00:31:36.700
What did you say? The man in the portrait?

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:37.800
Yes.

00:31:38.700 --> 00:31:41.100
Are you sure it’s him?

00:31:42.200 --> 00:31:43.500
Definitely.

00:31:43.860 --> 00:31:46.540
I saw that portrait so often I could clearly picture him in my mind.

00:31:46.730 --> 00:31:49.300
You, bastard! Son of a bitch!

00:31:49.460 --> 00:31:50.300
Get off me!

00:31:50.930 --> 00:31:53.540
I’m going to kill you!

00:31:54.860 --> 00:31:56.140
Khun Yai.

00:31:57.960 --> 00:31:59.060
But…

00:31:59.060 --> 00:32:00.020
But what?

00:32:04.200 --> 00:32:05.100
Nothing.

00:32:05.700 --> 00:32:09.300
It’s just…I can’t go back to work at the university anymore.

00:32:09.300 --> 00:32:10.900
All because of you, Sophee!

00:32:11.660 --> 00:32:13.740
Give me some money right now.

00:32:14.200 --> 00:32:16.160
Why should I? You messed it up yourself.

00:32:16.360 --> 00:32:19.780
If it weren’t for what you told me to do, I wouldn’t have ended up like this.

00:32:21.760 --> 00:32:23.500
Are you sure it was because I told you so?

00:32:23.960 --> 00:32:28.100
When I saw the way you looked at Kaewta, I knew right then how you felt about him.

00:32:30.960 --> 00:32:32.760
You also wanted him, didn't you?

00:32:33.130 --> 00:32:34.580
Don’t blame it all on me.

00:32:34.860 --> 00:32:39.700
If they expose me, I’m going to tell them you ordered me to do it.

00:32:40.700 --> 00:32:44.300
Go on then. But do you really think anyone will believe you?

00:32:44.980 --> 00:32:48.060
Don’t forget that I don’t have any problem with Kaewta.

00:32:48.460 --> 00:32:51.460
They’d rather believe it’s you who tries to threaten me.

00:32:52.660 --> 00:32:54.820
You’re more of a sly fox than I thought.

00:32:56.800 --> 00:32:58.780
I’ll take that as a compliment.

00:33:02.400 --> 00:33:06.060
Take it. But it’s not because I’m afraid of you.

00:33:07.930 --> 00:33:09.900
I just pity you.

00:33:16.260 --> 00:33:17.180
Get out.

00:33:19.700 --> 00:33:20.500
Fine.

00:33:28.600 --> 00:33:30.260
I see you’ve found my man.

00:33:33.060 --> 00:33:35.340
You lied to me again, Kaewta.

00:33:48.860 --> 00:33:51.220
How’s Khun Yai, Saen?

00:33:52.930 --> 00:33:54.220
I don’t know yet.

00:33:59.400 --> 00:34:00.800
They’re all here.

00:34:01.800 --> 00:34:04.730
We could only hope the same method would work on him again this time.

00:34:05.800 --> 00:34:08.420
I’m begging you, my buddha and holy divine gods.

00:34:08.420 --> 00:34:11.620
Khun Yai has been through a lot already.

00:34:11.620 --> 00:34:14.620
I don’t want him to suffer anymore.

00:34:14.860 --> 00:34:19.360
That’s right. He and Khun Kaew have finally met.
And things are going well lately.

00:34:20.730 --> 00:34:23.659
Talking about Khun Kaew, how is he doing?

00:34:24.460 --> 00:34:27.540
I’m wondering too, is he all right now?

00:34:27.540 --> 00:34:30.100
I’d better go make something for him to eat.

00:34:31.159 --> 00:34:33.699
Then, you and Sin should go take care of Khun Kaew.

00:34:34.100 --> 00:34:35.500
I’ll take care of everything here.

00:34:36.159 --> 00:34:38.159
Yes. Thank you, Dad.

00:34:39.100 --> 00:34:39.900
Let’s go.

00:35:07.160 --> 00:35:08.860
Why is Khun Yai in that room?

00:35:15.360 --> 00:35:17.100
Something is definitely going on.

00:35:20.660 --> 00:35:21.940
I must find out about it.

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:35.800
Saen.

00:35:36.460 --> 00:35:37.260
Yes?

00:35:39.560 --> 00:35:43.020
I don’t know if I’d be able to get through it this time.

00:35:43.500 --> 00:35:45.060
Why did you say that?

00:35:48.260 --> 00:35:50.020
I’m so worried about Kaew.

00:35:53.560 --> 00:35:55.260
Can you do me a favor?

00:35:55.700 --> 00:36:00.330
Please say it. I’ll go through hell and high water for you, Khun Yai.

00:36:29.360 --> 00:36:32.860
Khun Yai has asked me to give this to you, Khun Kaew.

00:36:37.400 --> 00:36:40.860
Me? Why?

00:36:42.500 --> 00:36:43.580
Please take it.

00:37:01.540 --> 00:37:02.340
A ring?

00:37:05.960 --> 00:37:13.460
He told me that if you see this ring, you might remember something.

00:37:18.160 --> 00:37:19.730
Remember what?

00:37:21.260 --> 00:37:22.220
I don’t know.

00:37:24.000 --> 00:37:25.160
Please excuse me.

00:37:57.260 --> 00:37:58.580
Looks familiar indeed.

00:38:01.560 --> 00:38:03.380
Where have I seen it before?

00:38:28.400 --> 00:38:35.560
What is wrong with me? Stop fantasizing, it’s just a ring.

00:38:38.400 --> 00:38:46.540
My heart still lingers in the old times when I used to be with you.

00:39:12.800 --> 00:39:15.980
Why did he keep talking in riddles?

00:39:17.300 --> 00:39:18.700
This ring too.

00:39:20.330 --> 00:39:21.740
Why would he want to give it to me?

00:39:24.000 --> 00:39:31.700
And why does he look exactly like that man in my dream?

00:40:13.330 --> 00:40:14.620
I have to know why.

00:40:28.130 --> 00:40:31.900
If it weren’t because of that bastard, Khun Yai would’ve never been like this.

00:40:50.130 --> 00:40:51.100
Dad.

00:40:51.760 --> 00:40:54.900
Sin, have you done what Khun Yai told you to do?

00:40:55.600 --> 00:41:00.000
Yes, Dad. But it seems Khun Kaew is still doubtful.

00:41:02.660 --> 00:41:05.380
Giving him a ring out of the blue like that, he’s probably surprised.

00:41:10.130 --> 00:41:13.340
I hope Khun Kaew will remember everything about his past life soon.

00:41:14.160 --> 00:41:16.580
Khun Yai has been suffering for so long already.

00:41:18.530 --> 00:41:21.160
So, how’s Khun Yai, Dad?

00:41:23.330 --> 00:41:24.380
He’s better now.

00:41:25.330 --> 00:41:26.660
What a relief.

00:41:27.200 --> 00:41:27.980
Sin.

00:41:27.980 --> 00:41:28.780
Yes?

00:41:29.300 --> 00:41:31.060
Make sure you take good care of Khun Yai tonight.

00:41:32.860 --> 00:41:34.380
You said it as if you’re going somewhere.

00:41:46.730 --> 00:41:51.530
Kaew, do you remember Luangta Cham who comes to receive alms in front of our house every day?

00:41:53.660 --> 00:42:00.100
Luangta Cham…I think Saen said his temple is quite close to our house.

00:42:00.300 --> 00:42:01.220
Yes.

00:42:01.620 --> 00:42:05.540
Many women at the market often go meditating with him at the temple.

00:42:05.540 --> 00:42:07.540
So, I asked if I could also tag along.

00:42:09.820 --> 00:42:14.580
Why do you want to go meditating, Mum?

00:42:16.300 --> 00:42:22.260
I believe you’re falling sick this time because of the karma you have done in the past.

00:42:22.940 --> 00:42:29.180
Maybe the merits from meditating could help protect you somehow.

00:42:30.860 --> 00:42:32.180
Aww, Mum.

00:42:34.860 --> 00:42:35.660
Kaew.

00:42:37.760 --> 00:42:43.620
Once you’re feeling well enough, you should go pay respect to Luangta.

00:42:44.980 --> 00:42:52.020
He said if you’re curious about anything, you can just ask him.

00:42:55.330 --> 00:42:57.220
Curious?

00:42:59.730 --> 00:43:01.540
What did he mean by that, Mum?

00:43:02.860 --> 00:43:07.700
I also don’t know, my dear. You have to find out by yourself.

00:43:18.700 --> 00:43:20.130
Geez, Sin.

00:43:20.300 --> 00:43:20.700
Yes?

00:43:20.700 --> 00:43:22.360
Slow down or you might get choked.

00:43:24.060 --> 00:43:25.130
You know what?

00:43:25.160 --> 00:43:27.260
Even if I get choked to death because of Miss Chan’s cooking,

00:43:27.360 --> 00:43:28.600
I’d surely die a happy man.

00:43:29.860 --> 00:43:33.580
Wow, Mum would’ve been so pleased to hear that.

00:43:33.600 --> 00:43:34.400
Her food is really amazing.

00:43:35.700 --> 00:43:40.900
Miss Chan has gone meditating, but she still makes sure our bellies are full.

00:43:40.930 --> 00:43:41.740
True that.

00:43:44.900 --> 00:43:47.420
Well, Sin…

00:43:47.420 --> 00:43:48.180
Yes?

00:43:48.330 --> 00:43:51.340
Here’s the dessert. I made it myself.

00:43:51.660 --> 00:43:52.340
Really?

00:43:52.340 --> 00:43:53.220
Yes.

00:43:54.330 --> 00:43:55.500
Do you want to try it?

00:43:56.330 --> 00:43:57.300
Is it for me?

00:43:57.300 --> 00:43:58.260
Yes.

00:43:58.260 --> 00:43:59.300
Can I try it now?

00:43:59.460 --> 00:44:00.260
Go ahead.

00:44:02.060 --> 00:44:03.500
I’ll have it then.

00:44:05.700 --> 00:44:07.980
Oh, wow. It’s so good, Khun Kaew.

00:44:08.200 --> 00:44:09.000
Is it good?

00:44:09.000 --> 00:44:09.860
Absolutely.

00:44:10.330 --> 00:44:12.460
Then please eat some more.

00:44:34.060 --> 00:44:35.530
Fine, I’ll quit!

00:44:36.800 --> 00:44:41.340
Can’t stay anymore. Have to go before anyone finds out about that brat.

00:44:44.460 --> 00:44:49.500
Acting all innocent when he was actually flirting with those eyes.

00:44:49.500 --> 00:44:53.260
[Laughing]

