Did I imagine it?

00:46:32.860 --> 00:46:36.140
How dare you, scumbag!

00:47:04.260 --> 00:47:06.940
How dared you touch Khun Kaew with those filthy hands?

00:47:07.460 --> 00:47:08.820
I’ll kill you!

00:47:13.860 --> 00:47:18.340
Remember, if you ever show your face in front of Khun Kaew again,

00:47:18.900 --> 00:47:20.700
I’ll hunt you down and break your neck!

00:47:21.900 --> 00:47:27.220
But if you dare touch Khun Kaew again, I’ll kill you!

00:47:46.460 --> 00:47:48.020
I’m fucking quit.

