No one can escape the hands of karma.

00:48:54.130 --> 00:48:54.960
Sin.

00:48:56.600 --> 00:48:57.580
Sin.

00:49:01.700 --> 00:49:02.980
Finally.

00:49:24.460 --> 00:49:25.420
Kaew.

00:49:28.930 --> 00:49:30.160
Sin, wake up!

